channel.title: The comeback of ~~( Hippiescape )~~ Try my new Emotes list! Official IRC, look!
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img171.imageshack.us/img171/7746/sitebanneruw9.jpg[/img] This is the final hippiescape installment, so i want it to go out with a good note. Join my new IRC channel! irc.moparisthebest.com #hippiescape Since you get to show off what you have done and so forth, im making my idea's public. V3 will be based on different spots then varrok and edgevil and fally. Those places won't even be accesable. Also: To reduce chances of lag, I will have boolean processes called at a much slower rate, thus less CPU/Ram used up. Revolutionary castlewars: I hope to throw away the castlewars of old, and add a new, more modern warefare to it. It's going to be much better then normal CTF, and with that, more fighting, and more oppertunitys to win. There will be no CTF, this war will be fought over command post, and keeping them will not be easy tasks. If you played Starwars Battlefront II, you'll get the idea. With each command post you hold, you get NPC fighters on your team, zammy and sara warriors. The more post, the more NPC's on your roster, and the less chance you have of loosing. Im debating to make this timed, or just have lives, or like SWBF2, a reinforcement count. More will come as I develop this. I'm going to create a one of a kind gameframe for a client ( i hope ) Im getting into graphics, and im going to be getting lessons from SWAT on clients, so yes there will hopefully be that one of a kind V3 client New areas and even a tutorial to boot. I'm also going to take a crack at serverside clan chat, and hopefully it will me quite more sophisticated then just
/createclan
I'm hoping for full NPC training, and Magic. That will be a large factor in the uniqeness in this project, becuase i'm going to focus on magic alot. More details later. Agility: Im working on agility for the first time. Let me tell you, im going to create a method for moving while you do an emote, hence such things as the hand holds, jump over fence ETC. More info later. A revolutionary skill will be unvailed, you will have to see it to believe the detail I'm putting in it Before anyone asks: No, im not recruiting people. This is a solo project, like v1 and v2 ended up being. I'll update my progress as ofton as I can (AOAIC). Progress: Not much, but: Ripped weapon handler.cfg out, and object.cfg,took into mind my own method for that. Somewhat done the tutorials New places initiated Messing around with magic and range projectiles Messed around with Castlewars some Perfect weapon emotes started - Will update AOAIC Updated news: The revolution to skills is here! Hippiescape will not rely soley on attack, strength, and defence. I will be unvailing: Weapon skills! Aquire your weapon.. train with it. Become skilled in it's arts and unlock faster hits, harder strikes and the special attack of the weapon! More will come out of this, but it's secret :) Post your thoughts on it if you want ( recomended ) Also, i'm a man of the people. Alot of you have played my v1+v2, if you have anything you would like to sugest, or have me improve, don't be afraid to post [/center] Download my improved emote list! 140 more emote ID's were added!
